name: Ecommerce-Application-using-Microservice-Architecture-Node-Js-RabbitMq-MongoDB
description: E-Commerce System Architecture with Microservices (Authentication, Product, and Order). RabbitMQ is the most popular open source message broker. RabbitMQ is lightweight and easy to deploy. It supports multiple messaging protocols. RabbitMQ has decent performance and a strong community. If your requirement is to process thousands of messages per second, I would suggest you go for something like RabbitMQ.
